{"id":"index","title":"現代 Web 開發平台","contents":"\n\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <!-- FULL HEADER BLOCK -->\n  <!-- BACKGROUND IMAGE -->\n  <div class=\"background-sky hero\"></div>\n  <!-- INTRO SECTION -->\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" id=\"intro\">\n    <!-- LOGO -->\n    <div class=\"hero-logo\"></div>\n    <!-- CONTAINER -->\n    <div class=\"homepage-container\">\n      <h1 class=\"hero-headline no-title no-toc no-anchor\" aria-label=\"Angular - The modern web developer's platform\" id=\"現代-web-開發平台\">現代 Web 開發平台</h1>\n      <a class=\"button hero-cta no-print\" href=\"start\">快速上手</a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n<!-- MAIN CONTENT -->\n<article>\n  <div class=\"home-rows\">\n<p>    <aio-announcement-bar></aio-announcement-bar></p>\n    <!-- Group 1 -->\n    <div layout=\"row\" layout-xs=\"column\" class=\"home-row homepage-container\">\n      <div class=\"promo-img-container promo-1\">\n        <div>\n          <img height=\"222\" width=\"340\" src=\"generated/images/marketing/home/responsive-framework.svg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"text-container\">\n        <section ng-should-translate=\"\" aria-labelledby=\"promo-1-title\" class=\"text-block promo-1-desc l-pad-top-2\">\n          <h2 id=\"promo-1-title\" class=\"text-headline no-anchor\">橫跨多種平台</h2>\n          <p class=\"text-body\">學會用 Angular 建構應用，然後把這些程式碼和能力複用在多種多種不同平台的應用上 —— Web、移動 Web、移動應用、原生應用和桌面原生應用。\n          </p>\n        </section>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <hr>\n    <!-- Group 2 -->\n    <div layout=\"row\" layout-xs=\"column\" class=\"home-row\">\n      <div class=\"text-container\">\n        <section ng-should-translate=\"\" aria-labelledby=\"promo-2-title\" class=\"text-block\">\n          <h2 id=\"promo-2-title\" class=\"text-headline no-anchor\">速度與效能</h2>\n          <p class=\"text-body\">透過 Web Worker 和伺服器端渲染，達到在如今(以及未來）的 Web 平臺上所能達到的最高速度。</p>\n          <p class=\"text-body\">Angular 讓你有效掌控可延展性。基於 RxJS、Immutable.js 和其它推送模型，能適應海量資料需求。</p>\n        </section>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"promo-img-container promo-2\">\n        <div>\n          <img height=\"222\" width=\"323\" src=\"generated/images/marketing/home/speed-performance.svg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <hr>\n    <!-- Group 3 -->\n    <div layout=\"row\" layout-xs=\"column\" class=\"home-row\">\n      <div class=\"promo-img-container promo-3\">\n        <div><img src=\"generated/images/marketing/home/joyful-development.svg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"400\" height=\"251\"></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"text-container\">\n        <section ng-should-translate=\"\" aria-labelledby=\"promo-3-title\" class=\"text-block promo-3-desc\">\n          <h2 id=\"promo-3-title\" class=\"text-headline no-anchor\">美妙的工具</h2>\n          <p class=\"text-body\">使用簡單的宣告式範本，快速實現各種特性。使用自訂元件和大量現有元件，擴充範本語言。在幾乎所有的 IDE 中獲得針對 Angular 的即時幫助和反饋。所有這一切，都是為了幫助你編寫漂亮的應用，而不是絞盡腦汁的讓程式碼“能用”。</p>\n        </section>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <hr>\n    <!-- Group 4 -->\n    <div layout=\"row\" layout-xs=\"column\" class=\"home-row\">\n      <div class=\"text-container\">\n        <section ng-should-translate=\"\" aria-labelledby=\"promo-4-title\" class=\"text-block l-pad-top-2\">\n          <h2 id=\"promo-4-title\" class=\"text-headline no-anchor\">百萬粉絲熱捧</h2>\n          <p class=\"text-body\">從原型到全球部署，Angular 都能帶給你支撐 Google 大型應用的那些高延展性基礎設施與技術。</p>\n        </section>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"promo-img-container promo-4\">\n        <div>\n          <img src=\"generated/images/marketing/home/loved-by-millions.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"455\" height=\"228\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <!-- CTA CARDS -->\n    <div layout=\"row\" layout-xs=\"column\" class=\"home-row\">\n      <a href=\"start\" class=\"card\">\n        <img src=\"generated/images/marketing/home/code-icon.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        <div class=\"card-text-container\">\n          <div class=\"text-headline\">立即試用</div>\n          <p>透過一個現成的範例應用來探索 Angular 的能力。不用安裝任何東西。</p>\n        </div>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </div><!-- end of home rows -->\n</article>\n\n  \n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - start\n-->"}